high_descs: Move to the center island.
Pick up the spoon from the island.
Move to the bowl on the island.
Put the spoon in the bowl.
Pick up the bowl from the island.
Move the bowl to the sink.
Put the bowl in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a spoon in it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the table immediately on your left.
Pick up the spoon with the blue handle.
Walk over to the bowl on the right side of the table you are looking at.
Put the spoon you are carrying into the bowl.
Pick up the bowl you just put the spoon in.
Turn to your left, walk over to the sink.
Place the bowl in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a spoon in a bowl into the sink.

high_descs: turn around and walk forwards to the kitchen stove, then turn left and walk to the middle of the kitchen island on your left
grab a spoon off of the kitchen island
move to the right a bit and then turn to face the kitchen island again
put the spoon inside of a bowl on top of the kitchen island
pick up the bowl off of the kitchen island
turn left and walk over to the kitchen sink at the end of the room
place the bowl in the sink there
anns.task_desc: place a bowl with a spoon in it inside the sink
